  "detailed_description": "Kitty Tom needs to go a long way to reach his home. However, the blocks of land that make up the path are completely out of order, making the journey more challenging. Your task is to slide the blocks on the terrain to create a path that leads the kitten from point A to point B.<br>In each scenario, there are three keys that the kitten must collect to open the door that leads to the next path. Help Tom reach his destination by guiding him through:<br><br><strong>The forest:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/9c9774f06ac6a70a6c0025a1b7ce5c22.poster.avif?t=1682296802\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/9c9774f06ac6a70a6c0025a1b7ce5c22.webm?t=1682296802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/9c9774f06ac6a70a6c0025a1b7ce5c22.mp4?t=1682296802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The beach:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/083381029af5f98c00c70b6fd98edeb3.poster.avif?t=1682296802\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/083381029af5f98c00c70b6fd98edeb3.webm?t=1682296802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/083381029af5f98c00c70b6fd98edeb3.mp4?t=1682296802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The village:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/e3dadba61eae8f4cec654a5a0b349b47.poster.avif?t=1682296802\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/e3dadba61eae8f4cec654a5a0b349b47.webm?t=1682296802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/e3dadba61eae8f4cec654a5a0b349b47.mp4?t=1682296802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>And finally to Japanese territory!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/3d5475b8767ce7578fe510d076e3f122.poster.avif?t=1682296802\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/3d5475b8767ce7578fe510d076e3f122.webm?t=1682296802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646030/extras/3d5475b8767ce7578fe510d076e3f122.mp4?t=1682296802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have fun during the <strong>80 stages</strong> of the journey!",
